          <h3>Design Process</h3>
          <p>We followed a comprehensive 8-phase approach: Research Phase (understanding user needs), Individual Ideation (diverse design exploration), Wireframes & User Flows (establishing architecture), Mid-Fidelity Design (refined layouts), User Research & Testing (validation), Iterative Revisions (feedback integration), High-Fidelity Design (polished visuals), and Final Interactive Prototype (seamless experience).</p>
